      "value": "A video from a TV broadcast with a male and a female news achor. They both stay in frame all the time.\n\nThe dialog from the male and female is as follows:\n\nSpaker_1 is the woman, and Speaker_2 is the man.\n\n[speaker_1][confused]: This is awkward! I guess the prompter ran out of ideas, and put us in this odd situation.\n[speaker_2][embarrassed] : But hey,  just because we are here, in a new video, doesn't mean our voices change. \n[speaker_1][excited]: Aber ich möchte mit dir schlafen.\n[speaker_2][happy]: I still have no idea what she said! Might be for the best [laughing]\n\nThe dialog with perfect lip-sync to the audio\n\n\nThey both smile at the end.\n\n\n\n\n"
